Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:48.13,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}虽然想去好好梳理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:55.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}但唯独真正想传达的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:02:01.72,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}纠葛不清说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:07.37,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}轻轻地深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.97,0:02:16.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}愿这温柔的希望能持续到永久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:19.73,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}能否看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:22.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:28.96,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}指尖描绘出的路标
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:32.04,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}能否传递到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:35.94,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}我愿今天也能继续欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:40.92,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}你明天也能充满笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:50.14,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}一定 一定
